### AGENT-CORE-API-002 | Report JSON 계약 조회
### Markdown source: docs/03_API/AGENT_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: GET /api/chat/{repo_id}/report
### 관련 기능 ID: AGENT-CORE-F-201
### 상태: 시작 전
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@repoId = 3f7cc46e-d954-83ab-9f12-013b0c9d2a1e

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/{{repoId}}/report
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 200 OK
### {
###   "code": 200, "message": "success",
###   "data": {
###     "summary": "프로젝트 마스터 요약", "stack": ["FastAPI", "Next.js"],
###     "fileMap": [], "recommendations": [], "heatmap": [],
###     "durations": {"parseSeconds":1.2,"embedSeconds":2.4,"agentSeconds":6.3,"docsSeconds":4.1},
