###   }
### }

### [오류] 아직 리포트가 생성되지 않음
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/report
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 401 UNAUTHORIZED / 404 REPO_NOT_FOUND / 404 REPORT_NOT_FOUND
### {"code":404,"message":"분석 리포트가 아직 생성되지 않았습니다.","data":null,"error":{"code":"REPORT_NOT_FOUND","detail":null,"field":null,"retryable":false}}
